{"tid":2429219,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Taylor Swift 批評 Netflix 喜劇 Ginny & Georgia 涉性別歧視","createTime":"2021-03-02T06:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T09:54:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2c34722229eb40b2ece78a93528274cd2d4b13","tid":2429219,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/97172e22c0ce427476f93c9904ca5f25/2021/03/e7702219c40fa200521344ef93198252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F97172e22c0ce427476f93c9904ca5f25%2F2021%2F03%2Fe7702219c40fa200521344ef93198252.jpg&h=d944fe54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國女歌手Taylor Swift批評串流平台Netflix的喜劇「母女姐妹花（Ginny &amp; Georgia）」涉嫌性別歧視。 <br />\n<br />\n劇集當中一幕，主角同母親討論到與男友分手的話題，期間有角色笑稱，對方換男友的速度較Taylor Swift還要快。Taylor Swift在社交網站上批評對白非常歧視女性，重提平台為自己製作、講述女性名人面臨公眾壓力的紀錄片，並特別提到現時正值3月的「美國女性歷史月」。 <br />\n<br />\n部份網民批評，Netflix節目羞辱背離傳統的性別期望的女性。「尊重Taylor Swift」一詞據報在Twitter上，一度成為熱門。 <br />\n<br />\nNetflix的官方網站特別提到，平台重視「包容與多樣」，去年更同聯合國婦女署合作，推出慶祝國際婦女節的影集，又指在2019年，Netflix原創電影的導演中，兩成人是女性。目前Netflix和劇集的相關人員尚未回應爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2381223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2381223&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2BTO5ApsLFANoEfWU0iq%2Bkc%3D&h=e1c4965e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2381223</a>"},{"pid":"f8ba4022638fac87d76e97ce9f60909f02dbe0fe","tid":2429219,"uid":203799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢又嚟料"},{"pid":"b969ed29871cd17fbe655b3d64bd9c3881dbc6f2","tid":2429219,"uid":152476,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"Netflix咁撚政治正確都奶野<br